      <title>希腊计划今年提前偿还欧元区救助贷款——消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/greece-plans-early-repayment-eurozone-bailout-loans-this-year-sources-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名政府官员周二对路透社表示，希腊计划今年提前偿还向欧元区国家提供的高达 50 亿欧元（53.4 亿美元）的救助贷款，以寻求在过去十年的债务危机后恢复正常。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/greece-plans-early-repayment-eurozone-bailout-loans-this-year-sources-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:17:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
