      <title>由于利息收入低于预期，DNB 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/norwegian-bank-dnbs-q1-profit-beats-expectations-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威最大银行 DNB 的股价在周二早盘交易中下跌 3%，此前该银行公布其核心银行业务收入低于预期，尽管该银行的盈利超出了预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/norwegian-bank-dnbs-q1-profit-beats-expectations-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:37:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
