      <title>AG 表示，加州将在“数周内”结束埃克森美孚塑料调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/california-wrap-up-exxon-plastics-probe-in-weeks-ag-says-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州总检察长周一对路透表示，加州将于夏季结束对埃克森美孚和化石燃料行业在造成全球塑料污染中所扮演角色的为期两年的调查，并决定是否对石油巨头提起诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/california-wrap-up-exxon-plastics-probe-in-weeks-ag-says-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
